        </div>
        
        <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-muted);">
            At Evergreen Livestock, we believe in the harmony of nature and farming. Our mission is to provide the community with the highest quality, naturally-raised livestock and premium organically-sourced feed. 
            <br><br>
            Our animals, including Goats, Ducks, Rabbits, and Pigeons, roam freely in open pastures. They are nurtured without the use of harmful chemicals or artificial growth hormones. 
            <br><br>
            We also provide carefully selected food items that ensure maximum nutrition. We are dedicated to transparent breeding practices, animal welfare, and ethical husbandry.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

